# Backpack (Blue Coral)

**Last Updated:** 2026-03-07

## Company Overview
- **Sector:** Crypto Wallet + Exchange
- **Status:** Unicorn target, recent B valuation

## Recent Developments (2025-2026)

### Major Funding Round (Feb 2026)
- **Valuation:** B pre-money (unicorn status)
- **Fundraising:** In talks to raise M
- **Focus:** Tokenization infrastructure push
- Source: [The Block](https://www.theblock.co/post/389141) (4 weeks ago)

### Company History
- **Incorporation:** April 2023 (post-FTX)
- **FTX Impact:** Lost .5M (88% of corporate treasury) on FTX collapse
- Continued building despite setback
- **Backpack Exchange:** Incorporated March 2023
- **Mad Lads NFT:** Launched on Solana (April 2023)

### Product Evolution

#### 2023-2024: Foundation
- Started with spot trading market
- Crypto wallet integration

#### Early 2025: Futures Launch
- Rolled out futures contracts
- Expanding beyond spot-only model

#### 2025-2026: Full Platform
- **Futures trading**
- **Spot trading**
- **Crypto lending** (varies APR, varies LTV)
- **Integrated wallet** (Solana, Ethereum, BTC)

### Team Background
- Founded by former FTX employees
- Experience from FTX collapse informed design decisions
- Focus on transparency and user protection

## Product Features
- Multi-chain support: Solana, Ethereum, Bitcoin
- Integrated wallet + exchange experience
- Lending/borrowing services
- Futures and spot markets
- Mobile and desktop support

## Strategic Direction
- Tokenization infrastructure as growth driver
- Building complete crypto financial services platform
- Learning from FTX collapse to build safer infrastructure
- Solana ecosystem focus (Mad Lads, deep integration)

## Competitive Position
- Differentiator: Ex-FTX team building "what FTX should have been"
- Strong Solana ecosystem ties
- Rapid product expansion (wallet → spot → futures → lending)

